jDashboard is a value monitoring system, written in javascript.

It is possible to define multiple namespaces, each with attributes which have:

  * Min/max
  * Gradient type (positive/negative/bipolar/neutral)
  * A current value
  * Units

The datatype can be polled JSON or JSON/[socket.io][1].

Release on github pending.


[1]: http://socket.io/
